title: Highest Risk of Catastrophic Expenditure for Surgical Care
description: In 2022, 100% of people in Ivory Coast were at risk of facing catastrophic expenditure for surgical care, the highest rate in the world.

title: Highest Risk of Impoverishing Expenditure for Surgical Care
description: In 2022, 100% of people in Ivory Coast were at risk of impoverishing expenditure due to surgical care, the highest rate globally.

title: Lowest Implementation of Key Services Promoting Market Competition
description: In 2024, Ivory Coast had the lowest score of 23.07 in implementing key services that promote market competition.
